            <scopecontent>
                <p>This is the ledger of a shoemaker, 1827-1836, with additional information on
                    miscellaneous household accounts penciled in 1890s. There are several newspaper
                    clippings inserted in the volume (regarding election results from 1908 and a
                    piece about members of a military regiment).</p>
            </scopecontent>


